o <br />\nposition Hong Kong as a regional hub for China&rsquo;s Belt and Road <br />\nInitiative and a key node of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau <br />\nGreater Bay Area integration project, Beijing&rsquo;s plan to establish <br />\na globally competitive advanced manufacturing, finance, and <br />\ntechnology center.<br />\n<br />\n報告摘要（英文）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual_Report%2FChapters%2FChapter%203%20Section%204-%20China%20and%20Hong%20Kong_0.pdf&d=5cca5s3p9ov1qVPWD0M9HdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ed2224f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf</a><br />\n香港繼續走上更加經濟一體化的道路<br />\n與內地。 <span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府一直在尋求將香港定位為中國一帶一路的區域樞紐倡議和粵港澳的關鍵節點<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大灣區</span>整合項目，北京的計劃建立具有全球競爭力的先進製造業，金融業和技術中心。</span><br />\n&lt;google翻譯&gt;"},{"pid":"7e9ce4bc1eeb5935785d518f054b73f80e1627dc","tid":905930,"uid":77905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"淘寶終於免運費?"},{"pid":"bdc8671b4c640be66edb758a9a6157d4c0bb7719","tid":905930,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e9ce4bc1eeb5935785d518f054b73f80e1627dc","tid":905930,"uid":77905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"淘寶終於免運費?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:13:41.000Z","msg":"諗太多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4c0798513a799b74ff77f1b49054c1ad462363","tid":905930,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}